Package: Primo
Type: Package
Title: Package in R for Integrative Multi-Omics association analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kevin J.", "Gleason", email = "kevin.j.gleason@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre")),
    person("Fan", "Yang", email = "FAN.3.YANG@ucdenver.edu", role="aut"),
    person("Lin S.", "Chen", email = "lchen@health.bsd.uchicago.edu", role="aut"))
Maintainer: Kevin J. Gleason <kevin.j.gleason@gmail.com>
Description: Implements methods to integrate multi-omics data to detect joint associations 
              and pleiotropy effects across multiple GWAS and/or QTL studies, 
              with possibly overlapping samples. 
              It can also be used more broadly beyond GWAS and QTL studies
              to infer multi-way associations using summary statistics 
              from multiple data types or sources.
